core:assignAction.core:comment: If we are here then Online PIN is required. If PIN Entry in progress is also set, then the user must have been prompted to enter their PIN, i.e. the PIN has already been captured during the EMV transaction and the call here just collects the PIN block. We need to flag this to the RequestOnlinePIN command.
